Field   Eagle Point Fields  Students $20/hr./field $20/hr./ field $20/hr. field $20/hr. field Campus $40/hour $100 per hour $40/hour $160/hour Off-campus  $60/hour $150 per hour $60/hour $200/hour Back to Top   Additional Information Special Rental Conditions Leisure Pool Leisure pool cost if group uses pool during open swim: $30/hr. Maximum 35 participants during open hours. Wet Classroom Wet classroom rental must be combined with a rental of one of the pools. Climbing Wall Prices reflect a 2 hour minimum and 3 hour maximum rental. Prices remain the same per rental. Rec Sports will provide all equipment, instruction, and staff necessary for the rental to be a success. Wall reservations must be scheduled outside of the regular climbing wall operating hours. Assistant Director of Outdoor Pursuits can adjust staffing requirements based on ages of participants, skill level, group size, and other factors that may affect the group rental. Additional Rental Fees Utility Fees Utility fees will apply to non-university groups during and outside of normal operating hours. Utility fees will not apply to student organizations and departments during normal operating hours. Rec Center utility rate: $65/hr. Staffing Fees Facility staff: $15/hr ($22.50/hr outside of rserved times). Group Exercise Instructors: $25/hr ($37.50/hr outside of reserved times). Custodial Fees $30/hr/custodian. Some events may require 2 (male and female) custodians and will depend on the nature and size of the event. Weekend events may be charged at time and a half. Audio/Visual Fees Projector system: $10/hr (Rooms 205, 207, and combined only). Table/Chairs Room 205 or 207: $20 set-up fee per event. Rooms 205 and 207 combined: $30 set-up fee per event. Portable tables/chairs: $1/chair and $4/table. Administrative Fee $20/hr reserved. Back to Top Facilities & Reservations UNT Recreational Sports Facilities General Reservation Information Space Available For Rent Activity Areas Additional Information Visit U